16/09/2005
THESSALONIKI, Greece -- Minister of Development Dimitris Sioufas says Greece could help foster investor interest in Southeast Europe.
His offer came during the 1st International Business Conference organised by Thessaloniki's HELEXPO and the Organisation for the Promotion of Foreign Trade.
Government and company representatives from countries in the region are attending the event.
(Greek Ministry of Foreign Affairs Web site, MPA - 15/09/05)
